# 🌤️ Weather App

A sleek, minimal weather application that shows the current temperature, humidity, and wind speed for any city using real-time data. Built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript** with API integration.

![Weather UI](./weather-ui.png)

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔍 Search for any city
- 🌦️ Display current weather conditions
- 🌡️ Shows temperature in Celsius
- 💧 Displays humidity
- 🌬️ Wind speed indicator
- 📱 Clean, responsive UI with modern design

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3 (with gradients & flexbox)
- Vanilla JavaScript
- [OpenWeatherMap API](https://openweathermap.org/api)

